# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:14
translate spanish jamietv1_917dd9af:

    # "I follow Jamie into the living room and sit down on the couch next to her."
    "Sigo a Jamie al salón y me siento en el sofá a su lado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:15
translate spanish jamietv1_48789a88:

    # "The show starts up pretty soon after we sit down, and I try to watch while Jamie talks through every scene, explaining who all the characters are."
    "El programa empieza poco después de que nos sentemos, e intento verlo mientras Jamie comenta cada escena, explicando quiénes son todos los personajes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:18
translate spanish jamietv1_f26b00c3:

    # "Over time, she moves closer to me so she doesn't have to speak as loudly for me to hear her during the show."
    "Con el tiempo, se va acercando a mí para no tener que hablar tan alto y que yo la oiga durante el programa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:19
translate spanish jamietv1_7488a7ce:

    # gnd "See Cyndi is the older sister and she was married to Winston, but they got divorced and now she's dating Elroy."
    gnd "Verás, Cyndi es la hermana mayor y estaba casada con Winston, pero se divorciaron y ahora sale con Elroy."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:20
translate spanish jamietv1_e33871b4:

    # gnd "The younger sister is Carolyn..."
    gnd "La hermana menor es Carolyn..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:21
translate spanish jamietv1_76d94bb8:

    # "She goes on like this for a while, giving me the recap of the last eight seasons of this show that I don't care about in the slightest."
    "Sigue así un rato, resumiéndome las últimas ocho temporadas de esta serie que no me interesa en absoluto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:22
translate spanish jamietv1_2078b7b8:

    # "I just watch her, my eyes roaming over every inch of her body, nodding along as her mouth moved, thinking about how it would feel to kiss those lips."
    "Yo solo la miro, con la mirada recorriendo cada centímetro de su cuerpo, asintiendo con la cabeza al ritmo de sus palabras, pensando en cómo se sentiría besar esos labios."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:23
translate spanish jamietv1_e50f84f6:

    # "I have a hard time taking my eyes away from her to watch the screen."
    "Me cuesta mucho apartar la mirada de ella para fijarme en la pantalla."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:24
translate spanish jamietv1_dec3d4b8:

    # "I think about putting my arm around her. I want to hold her close, to feel her warmth against me."
    "Pienso en rodearla con el brazo. Quiero abrazarla fuerte, sentir su calor contra mí."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:25
translate spanish jamietv1_1ebc9500:

    # "But I'm afraid of pushing too far, too fast, too soon after finally fixing our relationship."
    "Pero me da miedo ir demasiado lejos, demasiado rápido, demasiado pronto después de haber arreglado por fin nuestra relación."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:27
translate spanish jamietv1_4aa5af9b:

    # "When the show ends and the sappy music starts up while the credits roll, she looks up at me and I look into her eyes."
    "Cuando termina el programa y empieza la música sentimental mientras pasan los créditos, ella me mira y yo la miro a los ojos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:28
translate spanish jamietv1_0e8a8301:

    # "A moment passes between us. We don't say anything, but I can see that she likes me just as much as I like her."
    "Se produce un momento de silencio entre nosotros. No decimos nada, pero puedo ver que le gusto tanto como ella me gusta a mí."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:29
translate spanish jamietv1_d17d6173:

    # "I can see that she wants me to kiss her."
    "Puedo ver que quiere que la bese."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:31
translate spanish jamietv1_c26dfc22:

    # "I lean in, our lips only millimeters away."
    "Me inclino hacia ella, nuestros labios están a solo unos milímetros de distancia."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:32
translate spanish jamietv1_574266fe:

    # "Then the front door opens and Jamie's dad walks in."
    "Entonces se abre la puerta principal y entra el padre de Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:35
translate spanish jamietv1_9ebb9cac:

    # "He looks directly at me, his face immediately dropping into a bulldog-like scowl."
    "Me mira directamente, y su rostro se torce inmediatamente en un ceño fruncido como el de un bulldog."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:38
translate spanish jamietv1_ceb35d85:

    # "Jamie pulls away from me quickly and rushes over to him."
    "Jamie se aparta de mí rápidamente y corre hacia él."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:39
translate spanish jamietv1_eda53ec0:

    # gnd "Hi, Daddy. I made lasagna for dinner. There's some wrapped in foil in the fridge for you to warm up."
    gnd "Hola, papá. He hecho lasaña para cenar. Hay un poco envuelta en papel de aluminio en la nevera para que te la calientes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:41
translate spanish jamietv1_72f1a03e:

    # jd "Sounds great, honey."
    jd "Suena genial, cariño."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:45
translate spanish jamietv1_f2a9fe7e:

    # "He walks up to her and wraps her in a hug."
    "Se acerca a ella y la envuelve en un abrazo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:46
translate spanish jamietv1_dee4a8d0:

    # jd "It's late. Send him home."
    jd "Es tarde. Mándalo a casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:47
translate spanish jamietv1_1976ecec:

    # "With that, he walks past me into the kitchen without ever laying eyes on me."
    "Dicho esto, pasa junto a mí hacia la cocina sin siquiera mirarme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:51
translate spanish jamietv1_d4db5419:

    # pc "I guess it is late. I should get out of here."
    pc "Supongo que es tarde. Debería irme."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:53
translate spanish jamietv1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:54
translate spanish jamietv1_c2f845d0:

    # gnd "I'm sorry. I'm trying with him. I told him that you've changed, but he doesn't want to hear it."
    gnd "Lo siento. Lo estoy intentando con él. Le he dicho que has cambiado, pero no quiere saber nada."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:55
translate spanish jamietv1_ce223137:

    # pc "It's okay. I understand."
    pc "No pasa nada. Lo entiendo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:57
translate spanish jamietv1_6c7c60bd:

    # gnd "I had fun watching the show with you though. Maybe we can do it again sometime?"
    gnd "Aunque me lo he pasado bien viendo la serie contigo. ¿Quizás podamos volver a hacerlo alguna vez?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:58
translate spanish jamietv1_0691c9a4:

    # pc "I'd love to."
    pc "Me encantaría."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:59
translate spanish jamietv1_6260e3d8:

    # "I don't care anything about the show, but I definitely want to spend some more time alone with her."
    "No me importa nada la serie, pero sin duda quiero pasar más tiempo a solas con ella."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:60
translate spanish jamietv1_6ce29231:

    # "It had felt like a spark had ignited between us in that moment where we almost kissed, but now it's gone. I want to feel that again."
    "Había sentido como si una chispa se hubiera encendido entre nosotros en ese momento en el que casi nos besamos, pero ahora se ha apagado. Quiero volver a sentir eso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:61
translate spanish jamietv1_5a7eedfa:

    # gnd "Okay, well..."
    gnd "Vale, bueno..."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:62
translate spanish jamietv1_f08905dc:

    # pc "Yeah, yeah, I'm leaving."
    pc "Sí, sí, me voy."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:66
translate spanish jamietv1_17ddf074:

    # "She walks me to the door and we say our goodnights before I walk back over to my house."
    "Me acompaña hasta la puerta y nos damos las buenas noches antes de que yo vuelva a mi casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:67
translate spanish jamietv1_d1f5525f:

    # "If her dad had come in just a minute or two later, this night would have gone much better."
    "Si su padre hubiera entrado solo un minuto o dos más tarde, esta noche habría ido mucho mejor."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv1.rpy:68
translate spanish jamietv1_a07dd7b4:

    # "Even so, it wasn't too bad."
    "Aun así, no ha estado tan mal."

